WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.590
I was praying and the Lord showed me,

00:00:02.590 --> 00:00:02.600
saying,

00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:05.789
"I need you to pray for Italy."I

00:00:05.789 --> 00:00:05.799
asked,

00:00:05.799 --> 00:00:07.309
"What is going on with Italy,

00:00:07.309 --> 00:00:07.319
Lord?"and

00:00:07.319 --> 00:00:09.230
he showed me. I

00:00:09.240 --> 00:00:10.709
had that open vision again, and he

00:00:10.719 --> 00:00:13.150
showed me there is a massive

00:00:13.160 --> 00:00:15.990
volcano that is about to happen. I saw

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:19.310
a coastline on the water,

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:22.230
and there is a massive volcano there.

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:24.990
He told me this is going to

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:27.470
happen, and there will be signs

00:00:27.480 --> 00:00:29.589
right before there is a massive explosion.

00:00:29.599 --> 00:00:32.350
I saw this thing explode; it

00:00:32.350 --> 00:00:32.360
was

00:00:32.360 --> 00:00:36.310
huge. He kept having me pray

00:00:36.310 --> 00:00:36.320
over

00:00:36.320 --> 00:00:39.150
the water; there is something about

00:00:39.160 --> 00:00:42.069
the water around Italy. I

00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:48.510
believe it

00:00:48.510 --> 00:00:48.520
was

00:00:48.520 --> 00:00:50.270
right here where this volcano was, because

00:00:50.270 --> 00:00:50.280
Pompeii is right here. There is

00:00:50.280 --> 00:00:52.790
a massive volcano up here, and so

00:00:52.790 --> 00:00:52.800
when

00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:54.270
I was looking

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:56.229
in the spirit and it was showing me, I

00:00:56.239 --> 00:00:58.110
thought it was in this spot, but I

00:00:58.120 --> 00:01:01.029
believe it is probably further out. I

00:01:01.039 --> 00:01:03.630
started looking at where the massive

00:01:03.640 --> 00:01:06.830
volcanoes are in the water over in Italy.

00:01:06.840 --> 00:01:08.749
If you zoom out, I will show you there

00:01:08.749 --> 00:01:08.759
is

00:01:08.759 --> 00:01:12.109
a massive volcano, one of the

00:01:12.119 --> 00:01:15.230
largest, way down here.

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:18.429
Whenever I saw this massive

00:01:18.439 --> 00:01:21.749
volcano going off out of the water, it

00:01:21.759 --> 00:01:24.789
caused a massive tsunami wave. It

00:01:24.799 --> 00:01:27.270
exploded, and from the earthquake and this

00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:29.350
massive volcano, it was like

00:01:29.350 --> 00:01:29.360
a

00:01:29.360 --> 00:01:32.310
humongous nuclear bomb went off

00:01:32.320 --> 00:01:34.149
and it went up out of the water,

00:01:34.149 --> 00:01:34.159
causing

00:01:34.159 --> 00:01:36.550
a massive wave. The water

00:01:36.560 --> 00:01:39.109
rushed all over this area. It

00:01:41.880 --> 00:01:44.270
would cause a lot of devastation.

00:01:44.280 --> 00:01:46.350
One of these volcanoes out here,

00:01:46.360 --> 00:01:48.630
whatever it is the Lord is showing me,

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:51.069
it came up out of the water and

00:01:51.079 --> 00:01:53.550
caused all the air traffic around

00:01:53.560 --> 00:01:55.550
that area to be completely shut down. The

00:01:55.560 --> 00:01:57.709
Lord showed me that it would cost

00:01:57.719 --> 00:01:59.429
hundreds of thousands of deaths. When

00:01:59.439 --> 00:02:02.469
this happens, there will be signs, maybe

00:02:02.479 --> 00:02:06.510
even on the news in Italy, about some

00:02:06.520 --> 00:02:09.630
rumblings around that

00:02:09.630 --> 00:02:09.640
area—some

00:02:09.640 --> 00:02:11.670
earthquakes or

00:02:11.670 --> 00:02:11.680
tremors—to

00:02:11.680 --> 00:02:14.750
pre-warn that something big

00:02:14.760 --> 00:02:18.630
is going to happen. Do not ignore this;

00:02:18.640 --> 00:02:21.710
it is very serious. What

00:02:21.720 --> 00:02:25.430
I saw is very serious.

00:02:25.440 --> 00:02:27.390
If you start having

00:02:27.400 --> 00:02:30.070
a lot of tremors and you start seeing

00:02:30.080 --> 00:02:32.990
smoke or something going on, take

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:37.110
heed. Be forewarned;

00:02:37.110 --> 00:02:37.120
I am

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:39.070
trying to tell you.

00:02:39.080 --> 00:02:40.430
I was just praying in the spirit,

00:02:40.440 --> 00:02:42.910
worshiping, and all of a sudden, I was

00:02:42.920 --> 00:02:46.149
shot up. I was looking

00:02:46.159 --> 00:02:50.750
over Italy, and Italy was

00:02:50.760 --> 00:02:51.910
so

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:56.309
small. I was so high,

00:02:57.760 --> 00:03:00.190
looking

00:03:00.200 --> 00:03:04.190
down, and all of a sudden, I could see

00:03:04.200 --> 00:03:07.710
a

00:03:07.720 --> 00:03:11.830
black blanket over the water. It looked like a

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:14.830
very thick cloud,

00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:18.270
as

00:03:18.280 --> 00:03:23.430
black as molasses,

00:03:23.440 --> 00:03:27.430
very dark. They were

00:03:27.440 --> 00:03:29.229
all

00:03:29.239 --> 00:03:30.509
over the water,

00:03:30.519 --> 00:03:33.910
and I could see the

00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:37.190
black clouds going through all the

00:03:37.200 --> 00:03:42.589
houses. It looked like a smog

00:03:42.599 --> 00:03:44.990
going through, all around the

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:49.470
houses. I could see the rooftops

00:03:49.480 --> 00:03:51.789
because I was up high, and

00:03:51.799 --> 00:03:54.710
I could see the lights on in the

00:03:54.720 --> 00:03:55.630
houses.

00:03:55.640 --> 00:03:59.869
Above, the Lord pointed my attention

00:03:59.879 --> 00:04:04.830
to a massive circle, a

00:04:04.840 --> 00:04:07.869
humongous portal that was over the

00:04:07.879 --> 00:04:10.630
country of Italy. It

00:04:10.630 --> 00:04:10.640
was

00:04:10.640 --> 00:04:13.710
over where I told

00:04:13.720 --> 00:04:16.629
you the volcano

00:04:16.629 --> 00:04:16.639
is

00:04:16.639 --> 00:04:18.430
by

00:04:18.430 --> 00:04:18.440
Pompeii.

00:04:18.440 --> 00:04:22.749
Angels were coming out.

00:04:22.759 --> 00:04:24.550
There was this massive portal, and

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:27.189
the angels were

00:04:27.199 --> 00:04:29.950
coming out of it. The portal

00:04:29.960 --> 00:04:32.469
was like it was breathing; it was

00:04:32.479 --> 00:04:34.950
alive, swirling,

00:04:34.950 --> 00:04:34.960
with

00:04:34.960 --> 00:04:37.749
clouds all in it.

00:04:37.749 --> 00:04:37.759
It

00:04:37.759 --> 00:04:39.950
looked like it was opening up,

00:04:39.960 --> 00:04:42.150
and all of a

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:44.430
sudden, thousands of angels started coming out

00:04:44.440 --> 00:04:46.430
of this massive

00:04:46.440 --> 00:04:50.230
portal. They

00:04:50.240 --> 00:04:53.350
were all

00:04:56.430 --> 00:04:56.440
descending,

00:04:59.080 --> 00:05:02.189
lined up

00:05:04.280 --> 00:05:07.350
like soldiers

00:05:07.360 --> 00:05:10.110
coming out of this massive portal over

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:11.749
Italy. It looked like they were

00:05:11.759 --> 00:05:14.029
coming downstairs, but I could not see

00:05:14.039 --> 00:05:17.150
stairs. Through the portal,

00:05:25.400 --> 00:05:28.150
clouds were coming out as it was breathing

00:05:28.150 --> 00:05:28.160
and turning. The clouds were

00:05:28.160 --> 00:05:31.469
humongous and beautiful: pink,

00:05:31.479 --> 00:05:34.230
fluffy, blue,

00:05:34.240 --> 00:05:36.830
and

00:05:39.950 --> 00:05:39.960
purple.

00:05:42.600 --> 00:05:45.350
I believe it was heaven.

00:05:45.360 --> 00:05:47.790
These angels were all

00:05:47.800 --> 00:05:49.830
coming down

00:05:49.840 --> 00:05:52.469
and descending onto the earth.

00:05:52.479 --> 00:05:55.070
When they got to a

00:05:55.080 --> 00:05:59.430
certain place in the atmosphere,

00:05:59.440 --> 00:06:01.990
they started

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:05.070
to spread out like ants all

00:06:05.080 --> 00:06:06.670
over the place. They started

00:06:06.680 --> 00:06:09.029
scattering and coming down even

00:06:09.039 --> 00:06:12.469
faster onto those homes.

00:06:12.479 --> 00:06:14.950
Each angel

00:06:14.960 --> 00:06:16.790
was

00:06:18.360 --> 00:06:19.589
on a mission,

00:06:19.599 --> 00:06:21.350
moving at the speed of light.

00:06:22.880 --> 00:06:26.270
They all had beautiful

00:06:26.280 --> 00:06:28.510
robes and gowns on.

00:06:28.520 --> 00:06:30.189
It was the most amazing

00:06:30.199 --> 00:06:33.110
thing. The whole time, I

00:06:33.110 --> 00:06:33.120
was

00:06:33.120 --> 00:06:35.150
sitting here in this chair praying in

00:06:35.160 --> 00:06:36.830
the spirit,

00:06:39.840 --> 00:06:42.070
soaking it all in. I

00:06:42.070 --> 00:06:42.080
am

00:06:42.080 --> 00:06:44.350
trying

00:06:44.360 --> 00:06:47.390
to explain everything the Lord

00:06:47.400 --> 00:06:50.309
showed me in detail.

00:06:50.309 --> 00:06:50.319
I

00:06:50.319 --> 00:06:53.230
am

00:06:53.240 --> 00:06:55.790
going to take a side note

00:06:55.800 --> 00:06:57.350
here because I was asking the Lord what

00:06:57.360 --> 00:06:59.589
all that black smog

00:06:59.589 --> 00:06:59.599
is.

00:06:59.599 --> 00:07:01.629
He was showing me that

00:07:01.639 --> 00:07:04.309
there

00:07:06.589 --> 00:07:06.599
is

00:07:08.599 --> 00:07:10.950
a lot of trafficking in Italy

00:07:10.960 --> 00:07:12.629
that people may

00:07:12.629 --> 00:07:12.639
not

00:07:12.639 --> 00:07:14.589
know about;

00:07:14.599 --> 00:07:16.469
he was showing me there was a lot of

00:07:16.479 --> 00:07:19.670
corruption and trafficking.

00:07:26.520 --> 00:07:30.950
Those angels were coming

00:07:30.960 --> 00:07:34.350
down to these homes

00:07:34.360 --> 00:07:36.189
and making

00:07:36.189 --> 00:07:36.199
a

00:07:36.199 --> 00:07:39.230
motion with their

00:07:39.240 --> 00:07:41.390
hands,

00:07:41.400 --> 00:07:44.230
telling the people to

00:07:44.240 --> 00:07:46.589
leave, warning

00:07:46.599 --> 00:07:49.390
the people.

00:07:49.400 --> 00:07:51.790
Every angel

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:53.790
was

00:07:56.080 --> 00:08:00.390
waving for the people to come.

00:08:00.400 --> 00:08:02.790
They did this for

00:08:02.800 --> 00:08:04.550
several minutes. You

00:08:05.759 --> 00:08:07.869
could

00:08:07.879 --> 00:08:11.029
sense an urgency on their faces, a warning telling the people to leave. They did not say anything, but I could

00:08:11.039 --> 00:08:13.670
see from their

00:08:22.759 --> 00:08:25.070
body language that they were in

00:08:25.080 --> 00:08:29.710
a hurry. Suddenly, all

00:08:29.720 --> 00:08:31.389
of the

00:08:31.399 --> 00:08:34.790
angels stopped.

00:08:34.800 --> 00:08:37.269
I knew people were

00:08:37.279 --> 00:08:39.469
praying; I could feel the intercessory

00:08:39.479 --> 00:08:42.709
prayers from the saints

00:08:42.719 --> 00:08:45.110
interceding for

00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:46.870
Italy in the spirit, praying in

00:08:46.880 --> 00:08:48.389
tongues.

00:08:48.399 --> 00:08:50.190
You could

00:08:50.200 --> 00:08:52.829
feel the blanket of prayer coming out of

00:08:52.839 --> 00:08:55.269
that portal.

00:08:55.279 --> 00:08:58.230
Above

00:08:58.240 --> 00:09:00.230
where all

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:03.470
the black clouds were,

00:09:03.480 --> 00:09:05.150
you could feel the

00:09:05.160 --> 00:09:09.110
intercessory prayer going on.

00:09:09.120 --> 00:09:13.590
All of a sudden, all the angels froze

00:09:13.590 --> 00:09:13.600
and

00:09:13.600 --> 00:09:16.430
turned

00:09:16.440 --> 00:09:19.310
their bodies to look back up

00:09:19.320 --> 00:09:24.350
to the massive swirling light

00:09:24.350 --> 00:09:24.360
of

00:09:24.360 --> 00:09:27.310
the portal. They all looked at the portal,

00:09:27.320 --> 00:09:28.790
and

00:09:28.790 --> 00:09:28.800
then

00:09:28.800 --> 00:09:30.190
they

00:09:37.399 --> 00:09:38.949
started

00:09:38.959 --> 00:09:40.190
shooting back up into

00:09:40.190 --> 00:09:40.200
it.

00:09:40.200 --> 00:09:42.670
After

00:09:42.670 --> 00:09:42.680
that,

00:09:42.680 --> 00:09:47.829
the Lord took me

00:09:47.829 --> 00:09:47.839
to

00:09:47.839 --> 00:09:50.630
another part of the vision. He

00:09:50.640 --> 00:09:54.389
said, "I want you to focus on the canary."Brandon, what is

00:09:54.389 --> 00:09:54.399
the meaning of a

00:09:54.399 --> 00:09:57.790
canary in

00:09:57.790 --> 00:09:57.800
a

00:09:57.800 --> 00:10:01.150
coal

00:10:01.150 --> 00:10:01.160
mine?

00:10:01.160 --> 00:10:04.750
Study this out. I saw a yellow canary

00:10:04.760 --> 00:10:08.470
in a cage in a cave. I could

00:10:08.480 --> 00:10:12.069
see gas, which is

00:10:12.069 --> 00:10:12.079
normally

00:10:12.079 --> 00:10:15.230
invisible,

00:10:15.240 --> 00:10:18.990
like a smog coming

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:22.030
up out of the ground. The canary

00:10:22.040 --> 00:10:25.350
was swinging on a little swing

00:10:25.350 --> 00:10:25.360
in a birdcage

00:10:25.360 --> 00:10:27.870
in the spirit realm,

00:10:36.480 --> 00:10:38.150
chirping and

00:10:38.160 --> 00:10:40.710
making noise. Suddenly, I

00:10:40.720 --> 00:10:43.430
looked at the gas coming up,

00:10:43.430 --> 00:10:43.440
and when I looked back,

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:46.470
the canary was in the bottom

00:10:46.470 --> 00:10:46.480
of the cage, lifeless. This

00:10:46.480 --> 00:10:50.389
gas coming up out of

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:52.910
the ground

00:10:57.269 --> 00:10:57.279
in

00:11:04.790 --> 00:11:04.800
Italy—I

00:11:09.519 --> 00:11:12.269
do

00:11:18.920 --> 00:11:21.350
not

00:11:25.600 --> 00:11:29.030
know if it was from

00:11:29.040 --> 00:11:29.949
the

00:11:31.710 --> 00:11:31.720
volcano—but

00:11:34.279 --> 00:11:36.870
I saw

00:11:36.880 --> 00:11:38.910
hundreds of thousands of people go home.

00:11:38.920 --> 00:11:41.590
I saw a massive wave coming. The

00:11:41.600 --> 00:11:44.350
Lord said, "Pay attention to the water."I saw earthquakes in the water,

00:11:44.350 --> 00:11:44.360
but

00:11:44.360 --> 00:11:46.910
the

00:11:46.920 --> 00:11:48.470
people were not paying attention. In

00:11:48.470 --> 00:11:48.480
past visions,

00:11:48.480 --> 00:11:51.350
the Lord kept

00:11:51.350 --> 00:11:51.360
pointing

00:11:51.360 --> 00:11:52.910
me

00:11:52.910 --> 00:11:52.920
to

00:11:52.920 --> 00:11:55.310
the water in

00:11:55.310 --> 00:11:55.320
the

00:11:55.320 --> 00:11:57.629
gulf

00:11:57.629 --> 00:11:57.639
area

00:11:57.639 --> 00:11:59.670
by Pompeii.

00:11:59.670 --> 00:11:59.680
This

00:11:59.680 --> 00:12:00.990
is

00:12:00.990 --> 00:12:01.000
just

00:12:01.000 --> 00:12:02.790
what the Lord

00:12:03.990 --> 00:12:04.000
has

00:12:06.920 --> 00:12:08.990
been

00:12:13.199 --> 00:12:14.550
showing

00:12:14.560 --> 00:12:17.829
me for the past week.

00:12:21.160 --> 00:12:24.750
For three times now, the Lord has

00:12:24.760 --> 00:12:28.069
spoken to me about the electric grid

00:12:28.079 --> 00:12:31.829
in America, telling me to pray over the

00:12:31.839 --> 00:12:35.150
electric grid. This is very serious. I saw

00:12:35.150 --> 00:12:35.160
something

00:12:35.160 --> 00:12:37.710
like a cyberattack or a false

00:12:37.720 --> 00:12:40.310
flag attack.

00:12:50.760 --> 00:12:54.550
Power went out in New York and

00:12:54.560 --> 00:12:57.509
major cities. It was completely dark

00:12:57.519 --> 00:12:59.750
everywhere.

00:12:59.760 --> 00:13:03.710
He said, "You

00:13:03.710 --> 00:13:03.720
are

00:13:03.720 --> 00:13:05.509
not taking this seriously

00:13:05.509 --> 00:13:05.519
enough."He

00:13:05.519 --> 00:13:07.350
warned me that I need to pray about

00:13:07.360 --> 00:13:10.629
this more intently

00:13:10.639 --> 00:13:12.870
because of what is being planned.

00:13:15.680 --> 00:13:20.230
When the electric grid went

00:13:20.240 --> 00:13:22.389
down, for some people, it had the

00:13:22.399 --> 00:13:25.310
opportunity to be down for over

00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:29.670
three weeks. I saw a calendar and

00:13:29.680 --> 00:13:31.430
could see

00:13:31.440 --> 00:13:34.110
the days go by with people being without

00:13:34.120 --> 00:13:37.150
power. The Lord was warning me

00:13:37.160 --> 00:13:39.269
about these major cities and about this

00:13:39.279 --> 00:13:41.870
plot against America and the

00:13:41.880 --> 00:13:45.189
power grid.

00:13:45.189 --> 00:13:45.199
I

00:13:45.199 --> 00:13:46.990
am

00:13:47.000 --> 00:13:49.269
interceding for

00:13:49.279 --> 00:13:51.269
this on top

00:13:51.279 --> 00:13:54.150
of the Italy thing.

00:13:54.150 --> 00:13:54.160
I

00:13:54.160 --> 00:13:56.949
tried

00:13:56.959 --> 00:13:59.350
to tell you all

00:13:59.360 --> 00:14:01.670
a year ago about

00:14:01.680 --> 00:14:03.550
investing in a generator that

00:14:03.550 --> 00:14:03.560
has

00:14:03.560 --> 00:14:06.790
three fuel types—propane, gas, and

00:14:06.800 --> 00:14:10.230
natural

00:14:12.310 --> 00:14:12.320
gas—and

00:14:15.399 --> 00:14:18.749
finding ways to power your home

00:14:18.759 --> 00:14:20.790
through solar.

00:14:20.800 --> 00:14:22.749
I

00:14:24.990 --> 00:14:25.000
do

00:14:26.749 --> 00:14:26.759
not

00:14:30.160 --> 00:14:32.269
want to preach fear,

00:14:35.600 --> 00:14:38.670
but I get these

00:14:38.670 --> 00:14:38.680
warnings

00:14:38.680 --> 00:14:40.629
from the Spirit of God and

00:14:40.629 --> 00:14:40.639
they are

00:14:40.639 --> 00:14:43.470
very intense.

00:14:45.959 --> 00:14:47.670
For

00:14:47.680 --> 00:14:52.269
instance, I was once praying over an ice

00:14:52.279 --> 00:14:55.509
storm and he was telling me

